title: The WAT20W Water Dispenser Demo ►NewAir
description:
In this video we’re going to take a closer look at the WAT20W Pure Spring water dispenser from NewAir. 

The WAT20W is 100% BPA-free to provide pure, crisp clean drinking water. It includes a bottle spike for easy loading and spill prevention. The WAT20W provides hot, cold and room-temperature water from one nozzle. There is a reliable child-safety lock on the hot water button.

And the WAT20W is UL and Energy Star Tested and approved. The unit even has a convenient insulated storage cabinet. There’s also even a switch to disable the hot and cold water so you can control your energy usage. And the drip tray is removable and dishwasher safe.

The WAT20W also has a stainless steel water tank to provide crisp, clear clean tasting water. 

Thanks for checking out the WAT20W  Pure Spring water dispenser from NewAir.
